Blooms Taxonomy

Topic: Antas ng Komunikasyon (FILIP11)

*EVALUATION

>I conclude that many ways and strategies can be formulate in this topic by trial and error or understanding.

*SYNTHESIS

>Experiment some topics by using the other branches or related topics of the said lesson and by trial and error.

*ANALYSIS

>Distinguish the needs, the definitions/meanings, and the ideas/ knowledge related.

*APPLICATION

>Understand the lesson itself.

*COMPREHENSION

>Determine the importance and the uses.

*KNOWLEDGE

>Study/browse the background and the content.